# Template only — real file `worker-openai.env` lives on the machine that runs
# the pool (e.g. 192.168.9.252:/home/admin/claw-code/deploy/podman/worker-openai.env).
# Generate or refresh it on that host:
#   cd /home/admin/claw-code && ./deploy/podman/sync-worker-openai-env.sh
#   ./deploy/podman/sync-worker-openai-env.sh --restart   # after key/url changes
# Full image deploy also runs the same sync via deploy/server-252/deploy-one-click.sh
# Do not commit `worker-openai.env`. Author: kejiqing
#
# Typical contents after generation (OpenAI-compat via host claude-tap):
#   OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
#   OPENAI_BASE_URL=http://host.docker.internal:8080
